---
title: Plant-Based Protein Shreds Burrito Bowls with Pico De Gallo and Green Onion Rice
description: Tasty plant-based protein shreds take centre stage with green onion and lime rice as its co-star in this delicious dish. The fresh DIY pico de gallo makes a great extra!
